OL,3,CSeriously-ill children surprised with
OL,4,Conce-in-a-lifetime Disney trip
OL,6,FFamilies of seriously-ill patients
OL,7,Fhave been surprised with a once-in-a-
OL,8,Flifetime trip to Disneyland, courtesy
OL,9,Fof a mystery donor.
OL,11,FThe families of 13 children from
OL,12,FDerian House Children's Hospice in
OL,13,FChorley, Lancashire, were invited to
OL,14,Fshare their stories and videos,
OL,15,Fexplaining why they deserved the
OL,16,Fchance to win the holiday.
OL,18,FThey initially believed that only one
OL,19,Ffamily would be chosen. But they have
OL,20,Fnow been told that all 13 families
OL,21,Fwould be joining the adventure.
