OL,3,CSeriously-ill children surprised with
OL,4,Conce-in-a-lifetime Disney trip
OL,6,FVicky Ogg, mum to four-year-old Kacey
OL,7,FOgg, who visits Derian House
OL,8,FChildren's Hospice, said: "I can't
OL,9,Fbelieve it's happening, I'm still in
OL,10,Fshock."
OL,12,FShe continued: "We've never been able
OL,13,Fto take the boys abroad. It just
OL,14,Fhasn't been possible for a number of
OL,15,Freasons. They have gone through so
OL,16,Fmuch. What a beautiful thing for all
OL,17,Fof us families to be there to
OL,18,Fcelebrate in that moment. To know that
OL,19,Feach of us has a story, and everything
OL,20,Fwe've all been through, it's just
OL,21,Fbeautiful.
