OL,6,F"Kacey's older brother Brody couldn't
OL,7,Fstop dancing when we got home. We were
OL,8,Fcelebrating in the kitchen all night `
OL,9,Fgoogling photos of Disneyland and what
OL,10,Fit looks like ` and we carried on
OL,11,Fcelebrating even though it was a
OL,12,Fschool night. We're all just so happy.
OL,13,FTruly, from the heart, it's just such
OL,14,Fa beautiful thing."
