OL,3,CSeriously-ill children surprised with
OL,4,Conce-in-a-lifetime Disney trip
OL,6,F"Riziah didn't sleep that night, and
OL,7,Fin the morning she was screaming "I'm
OL,8,Fgoing to Disney!" at everyone she
OL,9,Fpassed. She's already asking when we
OL,10,Fcan go! We will be eternally grateful
OL,11,Fto the family who have made this
OL,12,Fhappen."
OL,14,FDad of 10-year-old Jacob Privett,
OL,15,FAndrew Privett, said: "We are so very
OL,16,Fgrateful to the donor. It's incredibly
OL,17,Fdifficult to put into words what this
OL,18,Fmeans but by giving us this amazing
OL,19,Fopportunity.
