OL,3,CSeriously-ill children surprised with
OL,4,Conce-in-a-lifetime Disney trip
OL,6,F"It will allow us to create memories
OL,7,Fwith Jacob and as a family which we
OL,8,Fotherwise wouldn't have been able to
OL,9,Fdo. When you have a child who is so
OL,10,Fpoorly the news you receive is often
OL,11,Fnegative and it is so nice to receive
OL,12,Fsomething positive that we can all be
OL,13,Fexcited about and look forward to."
OL,15,FKaren Edwards, Chief Executive at
OL,16,FDerian House said: "For our families,
OL,17,Fto be able to make magical memories on
OL,18,Fa Disney holiday is absolutely
OL,19,Fpriceless ` it truly means the world.
