OL,3,CSeriously-ill children surprised with
OL,4,Conce-in-a-lifetime Disney trip
OL,6,F"We are all overwhelmed by the
OL,7,Fgenerosity of our mystery donor ` this
OL,8,Fis an absolutely incredible gesture
OL,9,Fthat will always be remembered. Our
OL,10,Fchildren and their families face
OL,11,Fincredibly tough challenges every day,
OL,12,Fand for someone to make this dream
OL,13,Fcome true is beyond wonderful. We
OL,14,Fcan't express how grateful we are."
OL,16,FDerian House, based in Chorley,
OL,17,FLancashire, cares for more than 400
OL,18,Fbabies, children, young people and
OL,19,Ftheir families from across the North
OL,20,FWest and is open 24 hours a day, 7
OL,21,Fdays a week.
